Revision history for App-rshasum

0.8.0       2020-08-16
    - Add [ReadmeMarkdownFromPod]
    - Add "SEE ALSO" section.
    - Add whitespace in a warning.

0.6.4       2020-08-16
    - Avoid accepting leftover non-flag command line arguments
        - Instead of --start

0.6.3       2020-08-16
    - Handle open() failures on files (and subsequent binmode exception)
    more gracefully.

0.6.2       2020-08-16
    - Grammar corrections in the documentation.
    - Precompile --skip regexes using qr/$_/ .

0.6.1       2020-04-28
    - Require perl-5.016-or-above.
        - http://cpantesters.org/cpan/report/2e68abc4-8249-11ea-b61b-de5d1f24ea8f .

0.6.0       2020-04-19
    - Add more documentation.

0.4.0       2020-04-17
    - Add the --skip flag
    - Add the --start-path flag

0.2.0       2019-03-11
    - Avoid emitting a leading "./" prefix for files in the root.
        - Added a test for that under t/run.t .

0.0.2       2019-03-09
    - Improve the error handling and docs.

0.0.1       2019-03-09
    - First version, released on an unsuspecting world
